resources.string: v1.2.2 \n This change log is beta please press your "Back" key to return to the application.

From 4th July 2011, we no longer operate the Wellington Shuttle services. There are several alternatives availabe: 
 
 * The Wellington Airport Flyer Bus runs every 15 minutes and costs $8.50 one-trip. It has leather seats, air-conditioning and free wi-fi. You can find it just outside the baggage area, to the right. 
 
 
 * Take a taxi (preferably sharing with other Telecom folk) using one of our preferred suppliers (refer to the intranet).
